a big pile of dumb muscle who wanted to prove himself more worthy of inheriting his father's title so he sailed away from his home island to the sword coast to perform mighty deeds worthy of being put into song. He would disguise himself as a bard and sing about his own deeds under the name Barnjorn. His family was very much alive and happy and the only thing he had going for him was being good at swinging and ax. His motivation was being rich and famous.